Class Station

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility.Station
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StationWithDepartureBoard

    public class Station
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents information about a Station.

    IMPORTANT: Urban Mobility is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.

      • getDistanceToStation

        public int getDistanceToStation()
        Get distance from your current location to the station in meters. NOTE: it is available only when this Station comes from StationSearchResult when you search stations around you. It is implied that your current location was specified when requesting to search stations nearby with StationSearchRequest.
        Returns:
        distance to the station in meters, Station.DISTANCE_UNKNOWN if not available

        Returns:
        duration to the station in seconds, Station.DURATION_UNKNOWN if not available
